cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NGU to '192.168.70.132' creates an IP conflict with amf_ip_address, causing address collision and network interface binding failures.

du.explanation_en: Setting remote_n_address to an unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause connection failure in the F1 interface, preventing proper communication between DU and CU.
du.explanation_zh: 將 remote_n_address 設定為無法連線的 IP '10.0.0.1' 會導致 F1 介面的連線失敗，阻止 DU 和 CU 之間的正常通訊。
